250
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:39,520
it feels like they're giving over the reins to 
somebody else to handle everything from customer  

251
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:45,480
conversations, the product development, the 
personality of what this company needs to be.  

252
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:50,320
And so you want to be as close to it as possible, 
but I think you do start bringing PMs in when,  

253
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:55,560
one, work just isn't getting done without 
you, you are that bottleneck as a founder.  

254
00:20:55,560 --> 00:21:00,800
Or when people other than you are doing the 
core PM work at scale. So design and eng are  

255
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:05,560
